trans-unit.source: Performs composition for containers.
trans-unit.target: Utfører sammensetningen beholdere.

trans-unit.source: This class is used internally by <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen er brukt internt av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>

trans-unit.source: You should generally not use it unless you are authoring a container.
trans-unit.target: Du bør vanligvis ikke bruke det med mindre du lager en beholder.

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > This type implements the <xref:System.IDisposable> interface.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT] > Denne typen implementerer den <xref:System.IDisposable>grensesnittet.</xref:System.IDisposable>

trans-unit.source: When you have finished using the type, you should dispose of it either directly or indirectly.
trans-unit.target: Når du er ferdig ved hjelp av typen, må du fjerne den direkte eller indirekte.

trans-unit.source: To dispose of the type directly, call its <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A> method in a `try`/`catch` block.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil fjerne av typen direkte, kan du kalle den <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A>metoden i en `try` / `catch` block.</xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: To dispose of it indirectly, use a language construct such as `using` (in C#) or `Using` (in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil fjerne den indirekte, bruke et språk som `using` (i C#) eller `Using` (i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the “Using an Object that Implements IDisposable” section in the <xref:System.IDisposable> interface topic.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon, se "Ved hjelp av et objekt som implementerer IDisposable" i den <xref:System.IDisposable>grensesnittet emnet.</xref:System.IDisposable>

trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine"> </xref> klassen med de angitte alternativene.

trans-unit.source: An object that specifies options that affect the behavior of the engine.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som angir alternativer som påvirker virkemåten for motoren.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the current instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle ressursene som brukes av den gjeldende forekomsten av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Call `Dispose` when you are finished using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>.
trans-unit.target: Kall `Dispose` når du er ferdig med <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose` method leaves the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Den `Dispose` metoden forlater den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>i en ubrukelig tilstand.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>

trans-unit.source: After calling `Dispose`, you must release all references to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Etter kall `Dispose`, må du frigi alle referanser til den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>Slik saneringsoppsamlingen kan gjenvinne minnet som den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>ble bruker.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [implementere metoden fjerne](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid kall `Dispose` før du slipper siste referanse til <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Ellers ressurser den bruker vil ikke bli frigjort før saneringsoppsamling kall av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>objektets `Finalize` metode.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir uforvaltede ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine"> </xref> og eventuelt frigir administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre både administrerte og uforvaltede ressurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Previews all the required imports for the specified part to make sure that they can be satisfied, without actually setting them.
trans-unit.target: Viser alle nødvendige Importer for den angitte delen å kontrollere at de kan oppfylles, uten å angi faktisk dem.

trans-unit.target: Delen til å forhåndsvise importerer av.
